webwork-tex.statement: The function \[f(t) = \left(t,-t,t^{2}\right)\] has \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}} inputs and \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}} outputs. Thus it is of the form \[f\colon {\bf R}^n \to {\bf R}^m\] where \(n\) = \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}} and \(m\) = \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}}.
